Hi technoshaman777
&nbsp;
You need to download WebTorrent.Desktop. The link is in the menu bar. There is also some tutorials available on the stickied topics. After you've installed it, you simply click on the magnet icon on this page under the video player, and then it'll download the torrent. You can also add your own torrents, and then add them to KopyKate. They will play so long as they're seeding, and if codec settings are right.
&nbsp;
