I just encoded a 480p version. Link is in the description.. It'll take you directly to an external player. 
&nbsp;
Even though it's not 'on ZeroNet', it still doesn't make a difference because you're going to be using WebRTC one way or another. WebRTC is just as with any torrent client really.. get a VPN if you're really paranoid. WebRTC also does not reveal your IP, this is misinformation.
&nbsp;
EDIT: The only reason KopyKate exists is because sites that contain a database of magnet links are vulnerable to DMCA takedowns. However, because this site has no server, the magnet links will forever exist on the internet, and nobody can wipe them out no matter what. ;)
